## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="79b3f-1055">从给定`XmlNode`的读取器读取一个, 并将读取器定位到下一个节点。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="79b3f-1055">Reads one `XmlNode` from the given reader and positions the reader on the next node.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="79b3f-1056">此方法创建与读取器`XmlNode`当前定位<xref:System.Xml.XmlNode.NodeType%2A>在其上的匹配的类型。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="79b3f-1056">This method creates the type of `XmlNode` matching the <xref:System.Xml.XmlNode.NodeType%2A> on which the reader is currently positioned.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="79b3f-1057">(如果读取器处于初始状态, `ReadNode`则会将读取器推进到第一个节点, 然后对该节点进行操作。)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="79b3f-1057">(If the reader is in the initial state, `ReadNode` advances the reader to the first node and then operates on that node.)</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="79b3f-1058">如果读取器定位在元素的开头, `ReadNode`则读取所有属性和所有子节点, 直到并且包括当前节点的结束标记。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="79b3f-1058">If the reader is positioned on the start of an element, `ReadNode` reads all the attributes and any child nodes, up to and including the end tag of the current node.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="79b3f-1059">返回`XmlNode`的包含表示所读取的所有内容的子树。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="79b3f-1059">The `XmlNode` returned contains the sub-tree representing everything read.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="79b3f-1060">读取器位于结束标记后。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="79b3f-1060">The reader is positioned immediately after the end tag.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="79b3f-1061">`ReadNode`还可以读取属性, 但在这种情况下, 它不会将读取器推进到下一个属性。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="79b3f-1061">`ReadNode` can also read attributes, but in this case it does not advance the reader to the next attribute.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="79b3f-1062">这样就可以编写以下C#代码:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="79b3f-1062">This allows you to write the following C# code:</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
XmlDocument doc = new XmlDocument();  
while (reader.MoveToNextAttribute())  
{  
  XmlNode a = doc.ReadNode(reader);  
  // Do some more processing.  
}  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="79b3f-1063">`ReadNode`虽然使用特性值, 这意味着在对属性调用`ReadNode`后, <xref:System.Xml.XmlReader.ReadAttributeValue%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>返回`false`。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="79b3f-1063">`ReadNode` does consume the attribute value though, which means after calling `ReadNode` on an attribute, <xref:System.Xml.XmlReader.ReadAttributeValue%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> returns `false`.</span></span>  
  
   
  
